<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Knowledge on Ops Handbook</title><link>https://bpinelab.github.io/ops-handbook/knowledge/</link><description>Recent content in Knowledge on Ops Handbook</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://bpinelab.github.io/ops-handbook/knowledge/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Markdown</title><link>https://bpinelab.github.io/ops-handbook/knowledge/markdown/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://bpinelab.github.io/ops-handbook/knowledge/markdown/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="headings">Headings&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#headings" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Create headings&lt;/strong>: &lt;code># Heading 1&lt;/code>, &lt;code>## Heading 2&lt;/code>, &lt;code>### Heading 3&lt;/code>&lt;br>
The number of &lt;code>#&lt;/code> symbols determines the heading level.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>Example:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-markdown" data-lang="markdown">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#000080;font-weight:bold"># Heading 1
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#000080;font-weight:bold">&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#800080;font-weight:bold">## Heading 2
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#800080;font-weight:bold">&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#800080;font-weight:bold">### Heading 3
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="emphasis">Emphasis&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#emphasis" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Bold&lt;/strong>: &lt;code>**text**&lt;/code> or &lt;code>__text__&lt;/code>&lt;br>
Makes the text bold.&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Italic&lt;/strong>: &lt;code>*text*&lt;/code> or &lt;code>_text_&lt;/code>&lt;br>
Makes the text italic.&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>Example:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#f8f8f8;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-markdown" data-lang="markdown">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>**Bold** 
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#000;font-style:italic">_Italic_&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="lists">Lists&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#lists" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Unordered list&lt;/strong>: Use &lt;code>-&lt;/code>, &lt;code>*&lt;/code>, or &lt;code>+&lt;/code> to create bullet point lists.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>Example:&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Shortcuts</title><link>https://bpinelab.github.io/ops-handbook/knowledge/shortcut/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://bpinelab.github.io/ops-handbook/knowledge/shortcut/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="tab-operations">Tab Operations&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#tab-operations" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Open a new tab&lt;/strong>: &lt;code>Ctrl + T&lt;/code> (on Mac: &lt;code>Cmd + T&lt;/code>)&lt;br>
Quickly open a new tab to view a different page.&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Close a tab&lt;/strong>: &lt;code>Ctrl + W&lt;/code> (on Mac: &lt;code>Cmd + W&lt;/code>)&lt;br>
Use this to close the current tab.&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Switch between tabs&lt;/strong>: &lt;code>Ctrl + Tab&lt;/code> (on Mac: &lt;code>Cmd + Option + Right Arrow&lt;/code>)&lt;br>
Easily switch between multiple open tabs.&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="page-operations">Page Operations&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#page-operations" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>&lt;strong>Reload the page&lt;/strong>: &lt;code>Ctrl + R&lt;/code> (on Mac: &lt;code>Cmd + R&lt;/code>)&lt;br>
Reload the currently displayed page.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Prompt</title><link>https://bpinelab.github.io/ops-handbook/knowledge/prompt/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://bpinelab.github.io/ops-handbook/knowledge/prompt/</guid><description>&lt;div class="pageinfo pageinfo-primary">
